'''Seihakusai''' (青柏祭) is the annual {{ill|Reitaisai|ja|例大祭|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Reitaisai|qq=}} of {{ill|Ōjinushi Shrine|ja|大地主神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōjinushi Shrine|qq=}}, held every year in {{ill|Nanao|ja|七尾市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nanao|qq=}}, {{ill|Ishikawa Prefecture|ja|石川県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishikawa Prefecture|qq=}}, from {{ill|May 1|ja|5月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 1|qq=}} to {{ill|May 5|ja|5月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 5|qq=}}. It is one of the {{ill|Four Major Festivals of Nanao|ja|七尾四大祭|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Four Major Festivals of Nanao|qq=}} along with the {{ill|Okuma Kabuto Festival|ja|お熊甲祭|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okuma Kabuto Festival|qq=}}, {{ill|Mukōda Fire Festival|ja|向田の火祭り|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mukōda Fire Festival|qq=}}, and {{ill|Ishizaki Hōtō Festival|ja|石崎奉燈祭|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishizaki Hōtō Festival|qq=}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.city.nanao.lg.jp/kikaku-s/shise/sesaku/1sogokekaku/honpen/documents/kihonkeikaku_1_4_5.pdf|title=Basic Plan: Chapter 1, Arts and Culture|access-date=2024-08-04|publisher=Nanao City|page=88}}</ref>{{Refnest|group="Note"|The Ishizaki Hōtō Festival, {{ill|Nanao Gion Festival|ja|七尾祇園祭|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nanao Gion Festival|qq=}}, and {{ill|Nanao Port Festival|ja|七尾港まつり|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nanao Port Festival|qq=}} are sometimes also included in the four major festivals.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://yamaguchi-ev.com/ishikawa-event/1692/|title=Events in Ishikawa Prefecture in May|access-date=2024-08-04|publisher=Yamaguchi Corporation}}</ref>}}

